{"tid":2311753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"近期太多組藝人回歸...總有人要「犧牲」的SM本週音樂放送行程！網友：「為什麼SM不調整一下呢」","createTime":"2020-12-04T10:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:23:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0ec0d5167417401531af49dfb841cad0710d06","tid":2311753,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b56d83584d10af6fe5420a1408380617/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132089-887575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b56d83584d10af6fe5420a1408380617%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132089-887575.jpg&h=e325c1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來還有這種規定，不過SM年末真的各種趕進度，接下來還有Super Junior、太妍要回歸呢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂歌手在11、12月陸續回歸，原本本週有5組（BoA、KAI、NCT U（90's Love）、NCT U（Work It）、aespa）要進行打歌，但因為音樂放送每個所屬社出演的藝人是有規定的，《音樂銀行》2組、《音樂中心》3組、《人氣歌謠》3組。<br />\n<br />\n12月4日《音樂銀行》BoA、KAI出演<br />\n<br />\n12月5日《音樂中心》BoA、KAI、NCT U（Work It）出演<br />\n<br />\n12月6日《人氣歌謠》BoA、KAI、NCT U（90's Love）出演<br />\n<br />\nNCT U、aespa原本會出演《THE SHOW》，但《THE SHOW》本週停播，這也讓不少網友表示：「為什麼SM不調整一下」、「原來還有這種規定」、「果然是SM家內鬥毆達人」、「KAI的SOLO從8月就開始說了，結果到了12月是這樣」、「所以Super Junior什麼時候回歸」、「SM阿～你覺得這樣有趣嗎」、「SOLO就活動一週ㅠㅠㅠ」、「但aespa和NCT已經第2、3週了，照顧先回歸的人也沒錯」、「新人不再打一下歌嗎」等等。<br />\n<br />\n而SM年末真的各種趕進度，太妍確定在15日帶著迷你4輯《What Do I Call You》回歸，Super Junior也將在12月發行正規10輯《The Renaissance》。"},{"pid":"1a69ac5c142346c1bee99fbac84522c9c7ebdad0","tid":2311753,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"sm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5290e1fb87693804e84bb6f7335d73868d1983","tid":2311753,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a69ac5c142346c1bee99fbac84522c9c7ebdad0","tid":2311753,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"sm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"JYP&gt;SM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020ff5f4fcd92a4dc29a4bdc72473c04c142bcc9","tid":2311753,"uid":242554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"YG: 我一年放一隊"}]}